{"tid":940921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批美國會通過《西藏旅行法》外交部：粗暴干涉中國內政","createTime":"2018-12-14T10:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T11:22:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0a84c2417cb63061292d5afc78cd492740e9cc","tid":940921,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181214/_2018121417265499752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181214%2F_2018121417265499752.jpg&h=d5ed30a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國會參議院經口頭表決，一致通過《西藏旅行對等法》，懲罰禁止美國外交官、記者和旅客進入西藏的中國官員，禁止他們取得美國簽證。北京外交部發言人陸慷回應指，美國國會通過的有關法案是妄顧事實，更粗暴干涉中國內政，違反國際關係基本準則。中國對此堅決反對，並已向美方提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷強調，西藏事務全屬中國內政，不容任何其他國家干涉，同時若外國人士要進入西藏，完全可通過正常渠道辦理。他舉出2015年以來有近4萬人次美國人到訪西藏，數字充分證明美方透過此法案對中方的指責站不住腳。他更敦促美方採取有效措施，阻止法案簽署成法，以免對中美兩國關係及兩國在重要領域的合作造成損害。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院已在9月通過法案，目前等待總統特朗普簽署生效。法案將要求在90天內評估美國公民進入西藏的狀況，並要求每年比較進出西藏自治區、「四省藏區」即青海、甘肅、四川和雲南4省藏族聚居區，與中國其他地區，描述妨礙自由出入這些地區的種種措施，向國會提交報告，並要求明確指出阻止美國人進入西藏的中國官員。假如有中國官員向美國民眾施加限制，美方就必須禁止這些中國官員取得入境美國的簽證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/888181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F888181&d=ntJutaLORMfbBelMl%2FE2uMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=49816591\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F888181&h=68fde47a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/888181</a>"},{"pid":"61b408f53f9461b3f1098184e18a16be892b36e5","tid":940921,"uid":38904,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"人哋congress 過咗關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你就干涉美國內政嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256cbddae1dc530d844c65480934434ce8d5ccca","tid":940921,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"比唔比你入境係人地既內政黎喎屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c449c1aa38aae1a2b4b9c4c9146798dedaded3c3","tid":940921,"uid":70786,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"近4萬人次美國人到訪西藏<br />\n唔公佈埋拒絕入境人數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6c8a9ef2ad1d2ccebc74dfccbfdb4f2b2d2693","tid":940921,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"口交部錄音機今次唔啱用喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b8245221e891ce48da869fbde48306b9371225","tid":940921,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"其實支那外交部係咪請智障做都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎黎去去三篤屁"},{"pid":"f9dfa1fbb8cfdfa730a7eeb87527d5840ee22c51","tid":940921,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"一年幾次嚴正交涉?"},{"pid":"e80400481ad48750677be01985b64d0d349e87be","tid":940921,"uid":48735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9dfa1fbb8cfdfa730a7eeb87527d5840ee22c51","tid":940921,"uid":130879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"一年幾次嚴正交涉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"日日嚴正交涉"},{"pid":"0f3a70ef4f403408cf69a3ab993cc5df692d1c81","tid":940921,"uid":37524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"陸慷係咪已經被禁入境美國<br />\n嬲嬲豬?"},{"pid":"dc7f3ab61f576b67ba36ac441b5d9a597ca